  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You manifest a ravine of gravitational energy in a line originating from you that is 100 feet long and 5 feet wide. Each creature in that line must make a <strong>Constitution saving throw</strong>, taking <strong>8d8 force damage</strong> on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p><p>Each creature within 10 feet of the line but not in it must succeed on a <strong>Constitution saving throw</strong> or take <strong>8d8 force damage</strong> and be pulled toward the line until the creature is in its area.</p><p><strong><em>At Higher Levels:</em></strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 7th level or higher, the damage increases by 1d8 for each slot level above 6th.</p>",
